text: Araslanovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Araslanovsky Selsoviet, Meleuzovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 159 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 14 km from Meleuz, 3 km from Smakovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Meleuzovsky District
title: Araslanovo
